==Notable alumni or attendees== This '''list of Florida State University alumni''' includes graduates, non-graduate former students and current students of [[Florida State University]]. {{quotation|'''Alumni Status''' is open to all graduates of Florida State University, all former students of Florida State who regularly [[Matriculation|matriculated]] and left Florida State in good standing. If a former athlete earns notable non-sports related distinictions then they should be added to alumni portion.}}
